### PostgreSQL Integration

Database code lives in `{{ package_name }}/infra/db/`.

Alembic migrations live in `alembic/`.

Configure:

- `APP_DB_HOST`
- `APP_DB_PORT`
- `APP_DB_NAME`
- `APP_DB_USER`
- `APP_DB_PASSWORD`
- `APP_DB_DRIVER`
- `APP_DB_DRIVER_SYNC`

Runtime access uses SQLAlchemy `AsyncSession`.

The generated `Makefile` also includes:

- `make migrate`
- `make downgrade REVISION=-1`
- `make revision MESSAGE="add_users_table"`
- `make revision-autogenerate MESSAGE="add_users_table"`
- `make current`
- `make history`
